title: JF Musial (director)
description:
You might not know JF Musial's face but you probably know his work. He founded the YouTube channel formerly know as /DRIVE, directed APEX: Story of the Hypercar" and "APEX: The Secret Race across America". His new project is a docu-series called "Pikes Peak: On the Edge" . It follows six drivers prepare and race in the famous Pikes Peak International Hill Climb.  It's available on Motor Trend on Demand right now.

https://www.motortrendondemand.com/show/pikes-peak-on-the-edge/12707/
